     H            Y.                                                      ECM060
     F** BCER30 *************************************
     F*IT IS CHAIN IN UNIT PRICE M/F WITH  MONTHLY REPORT FILE      *
     F* A.SATOH                  1981.08.24         *
     F************************************* BCER30 **
     FMBEPP01 UP  E                    DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80USIME
     I                                        3   60UYYMM
     I                                        1   40UYY
     I                                        5   60UMM
     I                                        7   80UDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 F2MHIN
     I                                        1   5 F2MHN1
     I                                        6  10 F2MHN2
     I                                       11  15 F2MHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 @MHIN
     I                                        1   5 @MHN1
     I                                        6  10 @MHN2
     I                                       11  15 @MHN3
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSIME   8
     C           *IN09     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     09
     C                     MOVE PSIME     USIME
     C                     Z-ADD01        UDD
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE '*'       @KOJO   1
     C                     MOVELF2MHIN    @MHIN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KANR  10
     C                     Z-ADD0         @TANK  105
     C                     MOVE USIME     @JRHZ   80
     C                     Z-ADD0         @SRYO   70
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @CHK    1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @LOT    1
      *
     C           F2TOKU    IFNE 0094
      *
     C                     CALL 'BBHR10'
     C                     PARM           F2TOKU
     C                     PARM           @KOJO
     C                     PARM           @MHIN
     C                     PARM           @KANR
     C                     PARM           @TANK
     C                     PARM           @JRHZ
     C                     PARM           @SRYO
     C                     PARM           @CHK
     C                     PARM           @LOT
      *
     C                     Z-ADD@TANK     F2TANK
     C                     END
      *
     C                     UPDATMBEPP011
